rows.label: qst702301_msg0001
rows.name:
Have you seen a soldier named
Meknes anywhere? He's my
subordinate, but I can't find him.

rows.label: qst702301_msg0002
rows.name:
...I swear, he's not the kind of man who
would just disappear without a word. He's
a good guy who cares about his comrades...

rows.label: qst702301_msg0003
rows.name:
If you find out anything, could
you let me know? Any information,
no matter how small.

rows.label: qst702301_msg0004
rows.name:
No ships have left recently. He might
have headed for the capital, or be on
his way... He should still be in Iira.

rows.label: qst702301_msg0005
rows.name: I hope he's just lost somewhere...
